name: Banalism # 50
description:
Smartphone photographic series of founded-objects in everyday life. This project came out with the idea of self-challenging to photograph ordinary things in the most simple way, just see, observe and take the image instantly. On going project since 2013.

Year and Place of Taken: 2016, Munich, Germany

Dimension: 3163 × 2303
 Resolution: 300 dpi
